In mabor::backend

mabor::backend

Struct Autodiff

pub struct Autodiff<B, C = NoCheckpointing> { /* private fields */ }
Expand description

Enable auto-differentiation on a backend.

This works as a backend decorator, extending the functionality of any backend with backpropagation.
